  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<em>You shift between combat styles, combining them to increased effect.</em><br/><br/><b>Prerequisites</b><br/>Improved Unarmed Strike, two or more style feats, base attack bonus +6 or monk level 5th.<br/><br/><b>Benefits</b><br/>You can switch your style as a free action. At the start of combat, pick one of your styles. You start the combat in that style, even in the surprise round.<br/><br/><b>Normal</b><br/>It takes a swift action to begin or switch your styles.<br/><br/><b>Combat Trick</b><br/>When it is not your turn, you can spend 2 stamina points to take the free action to switch your style.",
